comments: Jones (UTA) moves forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Davis' (LAL) side/back as Davis receives the pass.
Olynyk (UTA) slightly extends forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Davis' (LAL) back as Davis receives the pass.
Davis (LAL) goes to, not through, Olynyk's (UTA) space and marginal contact occurs to Olynyk's front in the post.

James (LAL) overtly extends his right leg forward after the release of his jump shot attempt and initiates contact with Jones' (UTA) lower body, causing Jones to become dislodged following his shot contest.
Brown Jr. (LAL) is moving alongside Dunn's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during Dunn's drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Olynyk (UTA) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps before starting his upward shooting motion.
Dunn (UTA) brings his hands forward toward Davis' (LAL) back and marginal contact occurs as Davis elevates to retrieve the pass.
Dunn (UTA) brings his right arm forward and initiates incidental contact with Davis' (LAL) right elbow during his upward shooting motion..
Horton-Tucker (UTA) and James (LAL) engage and disengage with one another after the release of shot attempt.
Olynyk (UTA) releases his off-arm away from James' (LAL) side and marginal contact occurs as Olynyk steps back toward the perimeter.
Schroder (LAL) brings his hands toward Dunn's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs with Dunn's front as he drives inside the perimeter.
Schroder (LAL) brushes Dunn's (UTA) left arm, causing Dunn to momentarily lose control of the ball, which he quickly recovers.
Dunn (UTA) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps before elevating to pass.
Davis (LAL) brings his left arm forward at the end of the drive and marginal contact occurs with Dunn's (UTA) right arm after Dunn releases the pass attempt.
James (LAL) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Jones (UTA) and initiates contact with Jones' back prior to making contact with the ball during Jones' upward shooting motion.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) and Jones (UTA) each jump vertically alongside James' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during James' driving shot attempt.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) and Davis (LAL) each make contact with the ball, which becomes dislodged during the rebound prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Jones (UTA) is firming up over his right foot when marginal body contact occurs with Davis (LAL) during the drive.
Olynyk (UTA) contests Davis' (LAL) shot attempt and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Dunn's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Olynyk (UTA) continues to extend to the side prior to illegal contact occurring with Reaves (LAL) as Reaves attempts to move over the screen.
Olynyk (UTA) engages and disengages with Davis (LAL) as Davis moves underneath the basket to pursue the rebound.
Olynyk (UTA) extends forward and initiates contact to James' (LAL) front that alters his body trajectory during the dunk attempt.
Reaves (LAL) briefly has his arm around Jones' (UTA) upper body before correcting.
Jones (UTA) firms up over his right foot and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on Reaves (LAL).
Schroder (LAL) is retreating alongside Horton-Tucker's (UTA) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as Horton-Tucker drives into the lane.
Schroder (LAL) makes clean fingertip contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Horton-Tucker (UTA) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Possession is correctly awarded to UTA.
Vanderbilt (LAL) moves forward into Horton-Tucker (UTA) and initiates body contact that affects Horton-Tucker's driving shot attempt.
James (LAL) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps before elevating for the driving shot attempt.
Agbaji (UTA) is moving alongside James' (LAL) path when marginal body contact occurs as James spins back toward the lane at the end of the drive.
Jones (UTA) is turning away from James (LAL) when marginal body contact occurs as James finishes at the rim during the driving shot attempt.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) turns slightly as he establishes himself in Reaves' (LAL) path and he does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Olynyk (UTA) and Reaves (LAL) mutually engage and disengage with one another off-ball, and marginal contact occurs. As they disengage, they make incidental foot-to-foot contact with each other.
Schroder (LAL) brings his right hand toward Horton-Tucker's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs with Horton-Tucker's front as he changes direction on the wing.
Schroder (LAL) moves somewhat laterally prior to marginal body contact occurring with Horton-Tucker's (UTA) side during the drive.
Schroder (LAL) legally contests Horton-Tucker's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
